{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-initials/task-23","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Slušao/la sam zvuk i vežbavao/la izgovor <span class=\"highlighted-text\">g</span> početnih slova i slogova.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"zh-a1-learn-initials","challengeType":24,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">g</span> se izgovara zadnjim delom jezika protiv neba usta. Da biste vežbali, pokušajte da izgovorite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">g</span> i trebalo bi da osetite gotovo naporan vazduh ako stavite ruku ispred usta.</p>\n<p>Kada <span class=\"highlighted-text\">g</span> je praćen sa finals <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">e</span>, i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">u</span>, dobija slogove: <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ga</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ge</span>, i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">gu</span>.</p>\n<p>Hajde da vežbamo izgovor ovih slogova, zatim koristi <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ge</span> u različitim glasovima kao primer.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Pinyin</th>\n<th>Herufi</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">gē</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">哥</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">gé</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">格</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">gě</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">葛</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">gè</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">个</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-initials/task-23"},"questions":[],"scene":{"setup":{"background"